{
  "stem": "23832.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I didn't know what to do with myself.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I found myself-- my-- I'm confusing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My sister went to a clairvoyance woman.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she said, if you want, you have somebody that you're very worried about.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "If you want her to survive, she has to go south of Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "If-- You have two choices.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You can go to Grojec.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It's a small town that time, only 5,000.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And she could get through the war there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Or she could go further south to Kazimierz, a city.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But I decided, I'll better go to the one that's closer to town.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I don't need to travel in the train when everybody recognize me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] So I choose that one.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And there, I didn't know what to do with myself.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I thought I'll be a maid.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I went to a woman who was like referring you to households.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I came there, and, and she wasn't there because her daughter was working by through the Germans in a field.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And on the way back, she said, all the way in the top of the wagon filled with hay.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And she reached out for a cherry.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And she pulled the cherry, and she fell off and broke her spine.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Therefore, the mother wasn't occupied what she used to do.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "She was going crazy running around town and crying, and lost her mind or something.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "In meantime, I need to be somewheres to sleep, And I was sitting all day waiting.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Finally, the-- and there was a very poor, young couple, just married.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And, and they had nothing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I knocked on their door.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And I said, go and check if she's back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Go and-- she was above them, living above them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And she didn't come.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
